name: Arbinu
description: The Arbinu project aims to introduce individuals to the Arbitrum ecosystem through its fun and friendly mascot, Arbinu! The project is community owned and managed, with strict limits on individual holdings to promote decentralization and widespread adoption. By leveraging the power of memes and community-driven content creation, Arbinu aims to increase awareness and understanding of the Arbitrum universe, serving as a guide and companion to all Arbinauts along the way!
